headlines.description: — Bam Adebayo knows the Miami Heat have some work to do to climb up the standings.
headlines.shortLinkText: Adebayo, Butler lift Heat past Kawhi-less Clippers 115-110

events.name: Houston Rockets at San Antonio Spurs

headlines.description: — Keldon Johnson scored 32 points and the San Antonio Spurs snapped an 11-game losing streak by beating the Houston Rockets 118-109 on Thursday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Johnson's hot start helps Spurs beat Rockets, end skid at 11

events.name: Denver Nuggets at Portland Trail Blazers

headlines.description: — Jamal Murray’s 3-pointer with 0.9 seconds remaining lifted the Denver Nuggets to a thrilling 121-120 victory over the Portland Trail Blazers on Thursday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Murray's 3 gives Nuggets 121-120 win over Lillard, Blazers
